{
  "stem": "1042.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at night, he used to come up, 12:00 on the night shift, and called us in the corridor and to tell us what's going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He received a letter that because we are not delivering the amount what we supposed to, and there are 1,300 people working. the Gestapo will send-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Gestapo is-- was sending food, and that's for nothing.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they are not giving us what they're supposed to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he told us, and then they said, you should be prepared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got-- they're gonna one day, they're gonna come over, and they will, all the 1,300 people, they're gonna kill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1944? '44 and '45, in the beginning [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when he told us this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he says, listen, but here, have a look on the left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is a basement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The basement is loaded with ammunition-- all kind of ammunition you have there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And across the street from our factory, we saw people was-- were preparing graves for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was, you know, in such bushes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw they are going straight and preparing the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he said, it will come one day, they will call you out, like for appell, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They will not tell you what for they came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you should know, I will not be here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You should know, if they will call you, don't ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Run right away in the basement, and take any kind of ammunition, and you start the first.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You shoot to the SS, what they will come from, the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this way, some people from you, they will survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, if you will not do this way, so all of you will be gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
